title: Josh Flagg
description:
“Million Dollar Listing’s” Josh Flagg spills the tea on everyone from RHONY’s Sonja Morgan to Candy and Tori Spelling to Fredrik Eklund! He talks about his start in LA real estate, the first property he ever sold, and his YouTube channel and celeb interview show. Plus, Lala dishes on RHOSLC’s Jen Shah!
